de.dfki.embots.embrscript
Class EMBRScript

java.lang.Object
  de.dfki.embots.embrscript.EMBRScript
All Implemented Interfaces:
EMBRElement
public class EMBRScript
extends java.lang.Object
implements EMBRElement

Stores a sequence of EMBRPoseSequence elements. For the moment the only addition to a pure pose sequence is the addition of the time reset if you use createScript.
